tutu poisoning
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:sickness and possible death of farm stock from the eating of tutu.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: 1907 citation: toot-poisoning
